:CMT. This device definition is used to test PS output. 
:CMT. Only one font is available.
:CMT. This version was originaly used for testing %default_width().

:CMT. Definition file                 Device name
:CMT. ------------------------------------------------------
:CMT. PSSPEC                          psspec

:CMT. Corresponding driver
:CMT. definition file                 Driver name
:CMT. ------------------------------------------------------
:CMT. PSSDRV                          pspecdrv

